import { Box, Center, Heading, Image } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'
import GitHubCalendar from 'react-github-calendar'
const Github = () => {
  return  <Box>
  <Center>
    <Box w="50%" >
    <Heading pb={5} >Github Calender </Heading>
    <GitHubCalendar username="sp740881" />
  </Box>
  </Center>
  <Center>
  <Box w="40%" >
    <Heading pb={8} >Github Streak </Heading>
    <Image src="https://github-readme-streak-stats.herokuapp.com?user=sp&theme=vue&hide_border=true"></Image>
  </Box>
  </Center>
  <Center>
  <Box w="20%" >
    <Heading pb={8} >Github Language </Heading>
    <Image src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/top-langs/?username=devn5900"></Image>
  </Box>
  </Center>
  <Center>
  <Box w="30%" >
    <Heading pb={8} >Github Stats </Heading>
    <Image src="
https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api?username=devn5900&show_icons=true&theme=vue&hide_border=true"></Image>
  </Box>
  </Center>
  </Box>

}

export default Github
